title: Sips Tea ( Lisa Raye Interview and more)
itunes:title: Sips Tea ( Lisa Raye Interview and more)
description:
Today on the show we had Lisa Raye call in where she gave all the tea and cleard up some things, one starting with comments made about Nicki Minaj which the barbz were not happy about. Also she spoke on the beef with Nicole Murphy and so much more. Moreover, Charlamagne was not in today so we allowed our listeners to nominate someone for "Donkey of the Day" and next was topic time where we opened up the phone lines to see who they thought was wrong or right from an email Yee read about a man who was definitly not for spending money on a woman and her friends, when he just only offered to buy a drink for 1.
